  "title": "Technique to detect infection by Fusarium udum in pigeonpea before symptom appearance",
  "abstract": "The technique, using an electric current detects infection before the appearance of wilt symptoms. As the prediction validity of this technique is > 94%, it should prove useful in selecting individual plants for crosses in a pigeonpea breeding programme",
